            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD’s letter to Würtenberger has not been found. See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-11825.xml">letter from Leopold Würtenberger, 10 January 1879</ref>, and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-11844.xml">letter to Melchior Neumayr, 24 January 1879</ref>. Würtenberger worked on the phylogeny of Jurassic ammonites.</note>
